					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">My Clip notes on how to get a solid RPG with a 1/2 person team... Also given more fulltime or all out fulltime <br /><br />1.) use 6502BDD to do all your I kill boss X which gives me Drop Y to let me do Z plot points<br />2.) use a 6502 simulator + Genetic Algortihm to run 1000s of battles and balance monster numbers/rates etc<br />3.) palette swap to the max <br /><br />doing this should limit the amount of time spent on balance, code and leave you more time to make story and special effects. The game can be done with just place holder graphics and then you can farm out the designs etc, to people to get them done till you reach your ROM limit.</div>

