						<div class="postbody">Cliff's Notes (usually with  's, though I see the company now goes by cliffsnotes) are study aids. It's a condensed version of a large book, used by people who don't want to read the big book, but want to get a good grade on a book report in school.<br /><br />People sometimes say &quot;give me the Cliff's notes version&quot; when they want a shorter explanation.</div>

					
